0:
”Alexa Open J's Favourite Quotes”
”Tell Me A Quote”
”Give Me Something”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: j's favourite quotes
des:
Who is J? 

Well he is a guy that loves to respond to people with a quote from his favourite books and movies. Sometimes the quotes will be cheeky and other times they will be inspiring. 

Did J write all these quotes?

Of course not!! He just loves a good quote and has been writing his favourites down in notepads for years. Now J is letting the world in on his favourite quotes through this Alexa Skill

How many quotes are on this skill?

That's hard to say. J started with about 10 and will be adding more as he sees fit.

Is J a real person?

He is as real as the air you are breathing.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
